## 4.5 Diagram 5: Single-Subscription vs. Broadcast Stream Comparison

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    subgraph S1["Single-Subscription Stream"]
        S1A[Controller] -- one pipe --> S1L1[Only 1st listener\ngets all data]
        S1A -.blocked.-> S1L2[2nd listen()\nthrows StateError]
    end

    subgraph S2["Broadcast Stream (asBroadcastStream)"]
        S2A[Controller] -- pipe 1 --> S2L1[Listener 1\ngets all data]
        S2A -- pipe 2 --> S2L2[Listener 2\ngets all data]
        S2A -- pipe 3 --> S2L3[Listener 3\ngets all data]
    end
```

> [!WARNING]
> **Common Pitfall:** Calling `.listen()` twice on a single-subscription stream throws a `StateError: Stream has already been listened to.` Convert to broadcast first if multiple widgets must listen.

