- [ ] `Future.delayed(duration, fn)` — create a delayed Future.
- [ ] `f.then(onValue)` — success callback.
- [ ] `f.catchError(onError)` — error callback.
- [ ] `f.whenComplete(cb)` — always-run callback.
- [ ] `controller.add(data)` / `controller.addError(e)` / `controller.close()`.
