### 2.6 Real-World Engineering Utility

- **Startups** use unit + widget tests for fast CI feedback (sub-5-minute pipelines).
- **Enterprise apps** add integration tests for payment flows, onboarding, and accessibility.
- **Game studios** use the Flutter **Timeline view in DevTools** to identify jank (dropped frames > 16ms).
- **Healthcare/Finance apps** mandate widget + integration tests for regulatory compliance (HIPAA, PCI-DSS).

